<h1 style="color:rgb(15, 230, 158) ; text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px rgb(102, 102, 102); font-weight: 600;" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="100" data-aos-duration="800" >HELLO THERE!</h2>
<br>
<div  data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="100" data-aos-duration="900" style="letter-spacing: 2px;">
  <p>This is a blog website created by Arjav Parekh and Aryan Ringshia. Here latest blogs from the author are visible which are stored in a database and can be removed from the database directly.</p>
<p> A News button is created which displays Latest news articles via GNews API. To support faster creation of webpages we have used Express.js.</p>
<p>For database and creation multiple elements like navbar there is usage of MongoDB and Bootstrap respectively.</p>

</div>
